281680.title: Sox: A Family's Best Friend
281680.description: A new family is having difficulty adjusting, when an adorable dog comes into their life. Once his special powers are discovered, the local dog catcher and the (F.B.D.I) Federal Bureau of Dog Investigation will stop at nothing to get him.

293082.title: The Foundling
293082.description: A Russian classic. Natasha gets lost in busy 1930s Moscow after leaving home to chase her cat. She meets friendly strangers along the way -- many of them children --  and unintentionally changes their lives. A fascinating glimpse of Moscow prior to WWII.

314071.title: The Zigzag Kid
314071.description: A witty, spirited and action-packed adventure about an almost-thirteen-year-old boy named Nono, his world of confusions, fears and fantasies.....Nono has been brought up by is workaholic single father, a famous police inspector.  He longs to be as good a detective as his dad but constantly gets himself into trouble.  His free-spirited mother disappeared and died when he was little.  Gaby, his father's secretary, cherishes Nono ad recognizes the anguish of a child with a missing part.  Police mascot and his father's would-be-disciple, Nono struggles with a wildness he can't identify.  It comes from his mother.  Two days before his bar mitzvah, he is sent off to his uncle's to be straightened out.  Once on the train, the over-imaginative boy is given one last chance to prove himself.  Together with charming grifter Felix Glick, an old acquaintance of his father's, he travels to the French Riviera and enters a world of disguises, crazy pursuits, chanson and Zohara, a mysterious woman whose secrets will forever change Nono's life.

328392.title: Trading Mom
328392.description: Unhappy with their strict mother, three children cast an ancient spell that allows them to choose a new mother — only to find they loved the original.

332933.title: Fred 3: Camp Fred
332933.description: After ending up at the wrong summer camp, Fred makes the best of a bad situation and vows to help his fellow campers win the annual games.

342061.title: Pants on Fire
342061.description: A teenage boy tells white lies to get what he wants, only to discover that his lies have started to come true — and ruin his life.

342067.title: Zapped
342067.description: A teenager who struggles to adjust to her new stepfamily and school receives some help when a dog training app gives her the power to control boys.

371077.title: And You Thought Your Parents Were Weird!
371077.description: Things get out of hand when Josh's girlfriend contacts his father's spirit through a Ouija board and ends up trapping him inside his robot creation.

397556.title: Christmas Trade
397556.description: Just days before Christmas, a body swap finds a real estate lawyer at a cutthroat firm and his sixth-grade son walking in each other’s shoes.

401315.title: Summertime Christmas
401315.description: With the help of a little girl, two of Santa's elves attempt to pull a small town out of a depression and turn its children from naughty to nice.

419119.title: MVP: Most Valuable Primate
419119.description: A junior hockey team finds a surprising new teammate when a chimpanzee that recently escaped from an experimental lab stumbles into their practice.

432261.title: Agent Cody Banks 2: Destination London
432261.description: Adventure is his attitude, as Cody returns, masquerading as a musical prodigy to stop a former teacher gone rogue with an evil plan to rule the world.

432269.title: Just for Kicks
432269.description: Soccer-loving twins despair about their team’s chances when their mom steps in as world’s worst coach, so they recruit a mystery man to help them win.

439448.title: Baby Geniuses and the Space Baby
439448.description: An alien infant awaits rescue by a band of brilliant toddlers, after he crashes down on Earth and falls in the clutches of an evil villain.

439450.title: Baby Geniuses and the Treasures of Egypt
439450.description: A mysterious new case takes the baby detectives on a far-flung journey to Egypt where they discover secrets hidden deep within the pyramids.

451291.title: Santa Claws
451291.description: When Santa suffers a major allergic reaction in the middle of his delivery route, it’s up to a litter of kittens aboard his sleigh to save Christmas.

456528.title: Operation Christmas List
456528.description: Things don’t go as planned when 12-year-old Barney tries to capitalize on the holiday rush by buying all the stock of the season’s most popular toy.

457313.title: Sherlock Bones: Undercover Dog
457313.description: A 10-year-old boy goes to Catalina to spend the summer with his toy-maker dad and meets a talking dog who needs his help to crack an important case.

458078.title: Mac and Me
458078.description: A young extraterrestrial lost on Earth finds an ally in a wheelchair-bound boy, and in friendship, they find magic and a sense of where they belong.

460975.title: Saving Christmas
460975.description: Kirk Cameron starts in a biblical look at favorite time-honored traditions and celebrations, stressing the faith elements of the holy season.

465976.title: Camp New: Humble Pie
465976.description: A new camp coordinator arrives full of pride and competition. When the pranks get out of control, the kid coordinators learn humble life lessons.

466811.title: Invisible Mom
466811.description: It’s up to a young boy to stop the chaos, when his mom unwittingly drinks her inventor husband’s latest creation, an invisibility potion.

468616.title: The Elf Who Didn't Believe
468616.description: One of Santa’s youngest elves who wants to become a real boy steals Santa’s sleigh and meets a young girl who needs a heart transplant.

470331.title: Babysitters Beware
470331.description: A boy turns misbehavior into an art form to drive off potential babysitters until he meets his match in the form of a Harley-riding prison guard.

472182.title: Escape From Planet Earth
472182.description: When a heroic astronaut from a blue-alien planet gets trapped on notoriously dangerous Earth, his overly-cautious brother must rescue him.

484044.title: Valentina
484044.description: Valentina and her friends are fun-loving, teenage girls. They shop, they have sleepovers and they dream about their first true love. When they decide to throw a spring bonfire party, they never expected it would turn into such an adventure!

485941.title: Monsters at Large
485941.description: In this spooky family comedy directed by Jason Murphy, a teen task force that fights imaginary monsters finds itself face-to-face with the real thing.

485970.title: The Dog Who Saved Summer
485970.description: When Zeus accidentally destroys an important party, he gets sent to obedience school while a trio of bumbling burglars are planning a heist.

485990.title: Robo-Dog
485990.description: When Tom creates a new "Robo-Dog" out of spare parts and a technologically advanced battery, his old boss finds out, and stops at nothing to get it.

486933.title: Step Dogs
486933.description: After the owners of two mismatched dogs get married and move in together, these four-legged foes must team up to defend their home from burglars.

491071.title: The Substitute Spy
491071.description: A group of grade school kids discover that their substitute science teacher is a secret agent. They're about to get an education in fighting crime.

494725.title: Mr. Frog
494725.description: When a young girl discovers that her teacher has turned into a frog, she and her classmates vow to protect him until they can find a cure.

496977.title: Legend of the Christmas Witch (Dubbed)
496977.description: When a teacher by day, holiday sorceress by night is kidnapped by a vengeful toymaker, her students set out on a mission to rescue her and Christmas.

498145.title: The Ransom of Red Chief
498145.description: Two scheming men hope to strike it rich when they kidnap the rowdy 9-year-old son of a local banker, but they're in for a big surprise.

499039.title: Big and Hairy
499039.description: A local basketball team in a deep slump enlists the bigfooted skills of a teenage sasquatch who just wants to shoot hoops and fit in.

500355.title: The Runner From Ravenshead
500355.description: An all-children cast highlight a hilarious adventure about a clumsy janitor who takes a rocket car to get a prisoner away from wardens to freedom.

500835.title: Remote
500835.description: A 13-year-old boy, obsessed with making remote-control toys, puts up a fight when trapped in a vacant model house with three dimwit prison escapees.

504690.title: One Small Hero
504690.description: Stowed away on a camping trip for the school wilderness club, a young boy must use his wits in order to rescue the club from a pair of kidnappers.

513344.title: Time Toys
513344.description: When four twelve-year-old boys discover magical devices that make them better students and athletes, they're off on a daring adventure.

514362.title: The Emperor's New Clothes
514362.description: Only a little girl can tell the mortifying truth to an Emperor fooled by con-artists who sold him a special diamond robe they claimed was invisible.

515889.title: Pets
515889.description: Siblings, whose family farm is in the red, find a stash of stolen gold and are captured by bungling bank robbers. Can their furry friends save them?

518587.title: Standing Ovation
518587.description: Five friends decide to enter a national music video contest for tweens in this musical comedy about the power of childhood dreams and adventure.

519433.title: Funny Cats
519433.description: Laugh along with the most hilarious cats on the internet. These funny furballs are always ready to do something wild, adorable, and unexpected.

519921.title: Benjamin the Elephant
519921.description: A goofy elephant and his 9-year-old human companion must save the zoo, but it’s going to take all their clever, creative, and inspired thinking.

521851.title: A.C.O.R.N.S.: Operation Crackdown
521851.description: With the lives of his friends hanging in the balance, a crafty squirrel concocts a plan to retrieve a stolen nut supply from a corrupt corporation.

530383.title: Like an American Idol
530383.description: A young girl who wants to be a musician like her father writes a song to sing for a TV show after he is laid-off and sells his musical instruments.

531300.title: Diamond Dog Caper
531300.description: It’s a battle between man’s best friend and America’s most wanted when a clever boy and a dog take on a crew of diamond thieves.

531302.title: Elf-Man
531302.description: Super-hero “Elf-Man” helps some kids save their dad’s invention from a bumbling gang of thieves and have the best Christmas ever.

533467.title: I Think My Babysitter Is an Alien
533467.description: A young girl starts to notice some suspicious happenings among her family after her astronaut father brings back a powerful piece of asteroid.

535984.title: Perro de Hollywood (Doblado)
535984.description: Un grupo de amorosos chicos salvan a una megaestrella canina de televisión que se escapó porque en Hollywood solo lo quieren para sacar dinero.

549665.title: Adventure of the Treasure Boys
549665.description: Using booby traps and knowledge of the land, a pair of brothers try to foil a gang of criminals who are after their family treasure.

551841.title: Quigley (Doblado)
551841.description: Al morir, un archimillonario y bromista de lo peor reencarna en perro, lo cual aprovecha para enmendar los errores que cometió como humano.

552828.title: Chabelo Y Pepito Detectives
552828.description: Un comandante les pidió que infiltraran a una banda de robachicos y cuál será su sorpresa que los villanos son seres de otro planeta.

552975.title: Ozzy
552975.description: When his family goes on vacation, a beloved dog is dropped off at a fancy kennel, which turns out to be a canine prison that he must escape.

553665.title: Santa's Boot Camp
553665.description: Fed up with entitled kids, Santa’s elves go on strike and force him to bring six such brats to the North Pole to take their place in the workshop.

557087.title: Miss Minoes
557087.description: Beloved family classic about a cat transformed into a young woman who, while still seen as a cat by her cat buddies, helps a reporter defend animals.

560768.title: Uncle P
560768.description: Multi-millionaire hip-hop superstar Master P is thrown headfirst into fatherhood in the suburbs when he becomes the guardian of his sister’s children.

562738.title: Designer Pups
562738.description: A struggling fashion designer finds fame when she styles a celebrity and her two very stylish dogs, but an envious rival soon steals the pups away!

562864.title: Russell Madness
562864.description: A Jack Russell Terrier becomes an unlikely pro-wrestling champion, with help from his monkey trainer, when a man inherits his family’s sports arena.

565419.title: Chabelo Y Pepito en La Lámpara Maravillosa
565419.description: Pepito tendrá que evitar que la lámpara que compró, y que inesperadamente le concede toda clase de deseos, caiga en las malas manos de su padrastro.

565991.title: Konrad
565991.description: When a factory-made 8-year-old boy named Konrad is shipped by computer error to the wrong family, he fights the company recall in order to stay.

566311.title: Boy Genius
566311.description: After his brother is accused of stealing at their middle school, a whiz kid teams up with a local crime writer to bring the real criminal to light.

568622.title: Snow
568622.description: After a reindeer is stolen just three days before Christmas, Santa-in-training Nick meets a charming zoologist who just might be able to help him.

568623.title: Snow 2: Brain Freeze
568623.description: Following an accident, Santa wakes up in the hospital with amnesia. Now, his wife must figure out a way to find him and save Christmas!

568786.title: 3 Day Christmas
568786.description: A man baffled by the social disconnect between his three kids and wife takes the entire house off-the-grid for three days to reconnect as a family.

571516.title: Dear Dumb Diary
571516.description: A creative girl daydreams in her diary about what she wishes her life could look like, imagining it could include catchy musical numbers and dances.

571541.title: My Brother the Pig
571541.description: A teen and her nanny rush to find an ancient antidote to break a spell that turned her brother into a pig just before he was pig-napped by a butcher.

573632.title: Camp Cool Kids
573632.description: Two brothers at summer camp have to face-off during the annual games contests, except one is on the bullying team and the other is with the “dweebs.”

574354.title: Lenny the Wonder Dog
574354.description: A dog with the ability to talk joins forces with a young boy and a police officer to stop a mad scientist from taking over the world.

575946.title: Eco-Teens Save the World
575946.description: During a student Congress in Washington, D.C., four teens uncover a plot by a corrupt senator and his Big Oil donor to drill in a conservation area.

576110.title: Norm of the North 2: Keys to the Kingdom
576110.description: On call to New York and the Arctic, Norm must clear his name for a crime he didn’t commit and then stop a company from stealing his kingdom’s ice.

577597.title: Help I Shrunk My Teacher (English Dubbed)
577597.description: A boy tries hard to adjust at his new school, but things take a turn for the worse, when he accidentally shrinks his teacher to just six inches tall!

577624.title: Adventures at the Chocolate Factory
577624.description: When their mom goes away for the weekend, and their dad must take the kids to work with him, a feud with a rival chocolate factory causes mayhem

577632.title: Little Miss Dolittle
577632.description: Blessed with the ability to speak to animals, an 11-year-old girl steps in to save a baby elephant, who was kidnapped from her local zoo.

577685.title: Goat Story: The Old Prague Legends
577685.description: This hilarious traditional Czech tale tells of a naive young clockmaker, and his envious companion, who happens to be a sarcastic goat.

578043.title: C.h.o.m.p.s.
578043.description: An ailing security systems company is going down the drain when a young electronics genius invents C.H.O.M.P.S. - Canine Home Protection System. His invention is a robot dog, powerful and vicious when activated, which he hopes will stop a crime wave and help him win the security system owner's daughter.

579029.title: Pets 2
579029.description: The hilarious trio of animal pals snuggles up on the couch to watch cats being cats in the best way possible: silly, funny, and fierce!

579030.title: St. Paddy
579030.description: A darling leprechaun sets out with a simple goal: to make the world luckier by bringing happiness to people in the form of wishes come true!

584918.title: I Love Toy Trains - Oh No!
584918.description: A set of the best bloopers from the popular kids’ series, “I Love Toy Trains,” mixes hilarious footage, jokes,and original music for a fun joy ride.

586158.title: Cop and a Half: New Recruit
586158.description: A jaded detective is partnered up with a 12-year-old, who proves her worth when it comes to investigating crimes and understanding technology.

591071.title: Harriet the Spy: Blog Wars
591071.description: In the running for the title of official class blogger, Harriet makes the unwise decision to cull material from her secret spying missions.

591073.title: Bruno and Boots (Wizzle War)
591073.description: When a new assistant head-master starts imposing a set of draconian policies, the students of Macdonald Hall and Scrimmage Academy unite to oust him.

594157.title: A Bulldog for Christmas
594157.description: After a jaded college student is turned into a bulldog, she must learn the true meaning of the holidays with her family from a canine’s perspective.

595349.title: Aliens Next Door
595349.description: Transferred to a new job, the Peoples family arrive on the planet Bolognia. Feeling very insecure about the move, they become even more intimidated by the sight of their hosts who are green, spotted and have antennae! Almost as frightened are their new Bolognian neighbors Charlick and Mavo Zox. When little Benny Peoples gets "lost", he unwittingly brings the two families together.

610243.title: Operation Dalmation: The Big Adventure
610243.description: A girl enters her color-changing Dalmatian in a local dog show, but struggles with how to get his colors to appear normal for his big moment.

611725.title: Boys Klub
611725.description: A teenager is disappointed when his dad sends him up to his aunt’s house in San Francisco, where he meets a group of basketball hopefuls.

611824.title: Luis and the Aliens
611824.description: A boy at risk of being sent to boarding school due to his neglectful Dad - and three aliens stranded due to watching too much TV - must help each other out.

618283.title: Wiener Dog Nationals
618283.description: A dachshund runt rescue competes against America’s fiercest wiener dogs in a race that proves it’s unwise to underestimate the underdog.

618559.title: Gnomebrook
618559.description: Get a free pass to the annual Garden Gnome Convention in the sleepy mountain hamlet of Glenbrook, Australia where thousands compete for best in show.

619500.title: The Santa Trap
619500.description: To prove Santa Claus exists to her family, 7-year-old Judy manages to ensnare him in her new Southwest town where he winds up arrested as an intruder.

621256.title: The Dog Who Saved Halloween
621256.description: After a family moves into a new house, their mysterious neighbor’s home has strange lights coming from it, and their talking dog is on the case!

627923.title: Christmas Thieves
627923.description: A pair of petty criminals dressed as Santa and his elf try to convince two children that they aren’t thieves at all, but are in fact babysitters.

630834.title: The Man From Clover Grove
630834.description: When a toy company feels its business threatened by a local craftsman who makes and donates toys to orphanages, it hires a spy to steal his creations.

632198.title: Christmas Break-In
632198.description: Before Christmas break, a blizzard leaves 9-year-old Izzy stranded at school with a trio of bumbling crooks who have taken the custodian hostage.

633783.title: The Great Rupert
633783.description: The family of an out-of-work vaudeville performer is pushed into homelessness but their luck changes when a crafty squirrel unearths a stash of cash.

634390.title: The Canterville Ghost
634390.description: While on their dream vacation at an ancient castle, the Otis family encounters the ghost of its former owner desperate to be released from a curse.

635595.title: The Grump Who Stole Christmas 2
635595.description: When a woodland witch casts a spell to make the residents of Gnomesville forget Christmas, Santa enlists the help of the ELF Detective Agency.

638180.title: To the Beat: Back 2 School
638180.description: In this sequel, sisterhood is tested, new friends are made, and rivalries pop up as the students compete for a prestigious, paid summer scholarship.

639251.title: Cascabelito
639251.description: En la feria donde trabajan de titireteros, Viruta y Capulina sacan de apuros al huérfano Pedrín. Él se queda a vivir con ellos y les cambia su suerte.

640664.title: Jack Y Los Frijoles Magicos (Doblado)
640664.description: Jack consigue chamba como niñero y, para dormir a su travieso cliente, le lee el clásico cuento de hadas del chico que vende la vaca de la familia.

643945.title: Christmas Curfew
643945.description: When a pair of teenagers escape their curfew for a fun Friday night out, they fall right into the crossfires of a pair of goofy bank robbers.

652613.title: Valentine's Day Dance 2
652613.description: Beezbee the bee, Peanut the giraffe and Brooklyn the lion are all best friends here to figure out what is so special and fun about Valentine's Day!

652621.title: Cupid 2
652621.description: It's going to be a wacky Valentine'sDay for the ages as Cupid's arrow gets mixed up with a goofy videogame character's silly schemes!

654882.title: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
654882.description: Based on the hit children's book series, a third-grader makes her own fun for the summer after her initially fabulous plans don't come together.

665853.title: Cinco De Mayo Dance 2
665853.description: Besties Beezbee the bee, Peanut the giraffe and Brooklyn the lion visit everyone in town to find out how they're spending their Cinco De Mayo.

670338.title: P.U.N.K.S.
670338.description: A group of misfit teens steal a suit that gives the wearer supernatural strength, but also allows their body to be remotely controlled.

674868.title: The Incredible Genie (Español)
674868.description: Simon encuentra un genio dentro de una lámpara, pero los errores del genio en la concesión de deseos ponen a Simon en serios problemas.

675108.title: Seventeen Again
675108.description: When Willie's science experiment goes awry, it sends both of his grandparents back to their youth. Can he find a way to reverse the process?

676645.title: Verano De Arizona (Doblado)
676645.description: Brent Butler, un joven sabio más allá de su edad, y su hermano aprenden sobre la vida durante su tiempo en el campamento de verano.

680018.title: The Great Mike
680018.description: Jimmy and Speck own a horse which they use for their paper route. When a new race track is built in town, Jimmy challenges a horse racer to a race.

680065.title: Mr. St. Nick
680065.description: When his father retires and attempts to pass the throne to his son, a young man must choose between his family's legacy and his lavish lifestyle.

682075.title: Switched
682075.description: Tired of being bullied, Cassandra prays that her nemesis, Katie, the queen bee of social media, would know what it's like to walk a day in her shoes.

682797.title: Casper
682797.description: Seeing is believing in this adventure about a kind spirit in need of a friend and his ghostly uncles who want all “fleshies” out of their manor.

693740.title: Granny Nanny
693740.description: A pair of bored retirees try out a new role that inserts them in the lives of overprotective parents, hyperactive kids and all sorts of family mayhem.

694645.title: Doubting Thomas (Español)
694645.description: Thomas Miller, un niño de doce años conocido por contar historias, escucha un complot para secuestrar a la hija del presidente y decide detenerlo.

696367.title: Imagined
696367.description: After getting fired from her job as an imaginary friend, Kal attempts to fix one of her past assignments in his tumultuous adult life.

698084.title: The Boy Who Saved Christmas
698084.description: When Santa's evil twin kidnaps him with plans to reverse Christmas forever, he doesn’t count on a courageous group of boys undermining his scheme.

698086.title: Underdogs
698086.description: A young man and expert foosball player sets off on an unexpected adventure with the players of his beloved game, unknowing the consequences to come.

699020.title: Surviving Camp Analog
699020.description: An online prank-gone-wrong sends a group of YouTubing high schoolers to a rehabilitation camp where they must fight forces of established conformity.

699066.title: El Perro Que Salvó La Navidad (Doblado)
699066.description: Un perro poco confiable pero astuto frustra a dos ladrones torpes que intentan ingresar a la casa de sus dueños durante las vacaciones de Navidad.

700479.title: Ira Finkelstein's Christmas
700479.description: A Christmas-obsessed Jewish boy on his way to sunny Florida trades places with another boy on his way to snowy Christmastown, Washington.

702010.title: Lucky Dog
702010.description: A divorced father of two is dedicated to his kids, his job as an architect, and his dog, Lucky—who tends to be a bit overprotective.

706459.title: School of Life
706459.description: Ryan Reynolds lights up the screen as the charismatic Mr. D, a middle school teacher whose lessons extend far beyond the classroom.

706761.title: Micah & Jane: Bullies Beware!
706761.description: Fit for all ages, this kids’ comedy follows a group of students as they use elaborate pranks to maintain order in their elementary school.

707605.title: The Sneak Over
707605.description: A misfit fifth grader who finds camaraderie with a group of film geeks must locate his dad’s limited-edition VHS or risk being grounded forever.

708282.title: Agaton Sax: The Movie
708282.description: A digitally remastered Swedish adventure of doppelgangers, crime solving computers and criminal jazz bands with 1963 master detective Agaton Sax.

708390.title: My Grandpa Is a Vampire
708390.description: A boy from California goes to visit his grandfather in New Zealand, where he learns that the frail old man is a fanged flier by night.

713193.title: Chicos Miniatura (Doblado)
713193.description: Un joven adolescente compra una poci—n de crecimiento, pero resulta contraproducente.

715616.title: Alone in the Woods
715616.description: After climbing into the wrong van on the way to his grandma's cabin for Thanksgiving, ten-year-old Justin discovers he's riding with two kidnappers.

715622.title: Dude Where's My Dog?
715622.description: When his dog runs off and gets doused with a top-secret invisibility potion, it's up to Ray to find him before the kooky, suspicious neighbor.

723546.title: Like Mike 2: Streetball
723546.description: A small 12-year-old boy discovers Michael Jordan's old pair of basketball shoes that suddenly turn him into a streetball league star.

100000548.title: The Three Dogateers
100000548.description: Three dogs must defend their home from sneaky burglars who could ruin the holidays. The pups may even need a little help from Santa Claus himself.

100001260.title: Proyecto Navidad (Doblado)
100001260.description: Un escritor recuerda cuando él y sus tres hermanos unieron fuerzas para vengarse de los Hagbarts, los matones más malos de su escuela.

100001416.title: Hoot
100001416.description: When a housing development threatens a fragile species of miniature owls, three kids answer the call to think big, break some rules and take a stand.

100001427.title: How to Eat Fried Worms
100001427.description: On his first day at a new school, 11-year-old Billy inadvertently challenges the town bully by accepting a dare to eat ten worms in a single day.

100001500.title: Alice Upside Down
100001500.description: When her father moves the family to a new town, an insecure 6th grader escapes into her vivid fantasy life while dealing with growing pains.

100001925.title: Mister Twister: Class of Fun
100001925.description: A substitute teacher with a whimsical and unorthodox approach to education bonds with his new class while clashing with the school’s strict principal.

100002264.title: Farm Days
100002264.description: This charming and witty rendition of “Old MacDonald Had a Farm” tells the story of a family that discovers the true meaning of home.

100002797.title: Kung Fu Boys
100002797.description: A Chinese-American problem child with a superhero dream becomes involved in an international crime when he’s sent to Shenzhen to live with his uncle.

02405.title: Undercover High
02405.description: Undercover High is a half-hour, hidden camera show for teens, that takes the world of prank television and brings it to the one place that kids will never expect it - their own high school!

03858.title: Get Ace
03858.description: A nerdy kid becomes super cool after he sits in the wrong dentist’s chair and says the wrong secret codeword that makes his braces ultra high-tech.

0300005302.title: Lucky Fred (Español)
0300005302.description: Fred recibió un robot que se transforma en lo que él quiera, pero no era para él, sino para su vecina, agente secreto de seguridad intergaláctica.

04373.title: Verano Azul
04373.description: Esta serie trata sobre las aventuras de un grupo de jovenes durante sus vacaciones de verano en una pequena ciudad en la costa sur de Espana. Los siete ninos: Quique, Javi, Pancho, Bea, Desi, Tito y Pirana, conocen a dos adultos con quienes comparten muchas experiencias nuevas, Julia, una pintora, y Chanquete, un marinero retirado que vive en un bote en un barco. cumbre.

04364.title: SheZow
04364.description: An extreme 12-year-old with an attitude inherits his late aunt’s ring and turns him into a female superhero with comic results.

0816.title: Gagsters
0816.description: The famous team of kid pranksters tricks you and makes you laugh!

04853.title: Animal Crackers (Español)
04853.description: Una pandilla de extravagantes animales salvajes se encuentran en todo tipo de aventuras en un reino salvaje donde las cosas son salvajes y neuróticas.

01084.title: Debra!
01084.description: The funny and vibrant live action series DEBRA! follows an energetic girl named Debra Carnegie Cameron Delong who has a mission to improve the world. Have you seen the World? Its big and amazing, but with an injection of teen enthusiasm it could be perfect!  Debra applies her big imagination to improving her school, her community and her friends lives while she is on a mission to bring back a stronger sense of community to Camfield.

02251.title: Kid's Town
02251.description: A funny family friendly show that follows father and son as they move to a new town, make new friends and clash heads with schoolyard bullies and an overbearing mayor.

0300007368.title: Monty & Co
0300007368.description: This delightful musical puppet sitcom addresses emotions that preschoolers experience and how to deal with them, while mixing in silly jokes.

0300005299.title: The Fairytale Detective Sandra (Español)
0300005299.description: Sandra es una niña que heredó de su abuelo la labor de detective para resolver todos los misterios en el mundo paralelo de los cuentos de hadas.

0300005045.title: My Uncle Silas
0300005045.description: A boisterous uncle takes care of his 10-year-old nephew for the summer in this turn-of-the-century drama.

04532.title: Chicken Girls
04532.description: Rhyme and her friends—known by their 'ship name, "The Chicken Girls"—have been dancing together forever. But this year, everything's changing...

0300008259.title: The Little Rascals Best of Our Gang (In Color)
0300008259.description: Join Spanky, Alfalfa, Buckwheat, Stymie, and Porky as they pal around, going on adventures and learning about the world together.

0300006648.title: The Chuckie Perez Show
0300006648.description: This late-night variety talk show, hosted by Chuckie Perez, features a blend of family-friendly interviews, stand-up comedy, and musical guests.

04358.title: The New Archies
04358.description: Join the mishaps and adventures of Archie and his pals: Jughead, Betty, Veronica, Reggie, Moose, and the rest of the Riverdale High gang.

0300008173.title: The Daltons
0300008173.description: Four brothers attempt to bust out of jail in this hilarious animated series that depicts creativity, ingenuity, and some good ol’ physical comedy!

02301.title: Edison Twins
02301.description: Tom and Annie Edison are twins who share an enthusiasm for science, problem solving and adventure.

04048.title: Barney Google & Snuffy Smith
04048.description: Animated series, based on the classic cartoon strip, about a hilariously feisty and cranky band of family and friends living in the backwoods hills.

0300007091.title: The Wannabes
0300007091.description: This comedy sitcom follows six performing art school tweens who "wanna be" pop stars, even if it they have to dressing up like fruit and rocking out in a local cafe.

0300004681.title: Altair in Starland
0300004681.description: The fantastic adventures of a young boy and his best friend on a star planet where roller coasters make themselves and stars in the sky tell jokes.

0300008603.title: The Plant
0300008603.description: This Detroit show depicts the struggles and joys of a long-term job where you quickly become family with your coworkers, and drama ensues.

02089.title: Best Ed
02089.description:
Best Ed is about the unlikely friendship between a dog named Ed and a squirrel named Buddy. Ed wakes up every morning to be the best Ed he can be, even though it drives Buddy bonkers. But for every funny blunder Buddy suffers, thanks to Ed’s cloying good deeds, Buddy knows that…although it’s hard to live with Ed…it’s harder to live without him. They’re not just friends, they’re best friends.
Meet the new odd couple for kids…one best Buddy. And one Best Ed!

0386.title: The Weird Al Show
0386.description: Yankovics signature warped comedy, original songs, TV and movie spoofs, offbeat animation, and ability to attract a wonderful and motley collection of special surprise guests are what made The Weird Al Show a Saturday morning hit.

01791.title: Pigs Next Door
01791.description: When a farmer decides to move, he gives his land to his loyal pigs: father Phil, mother Clara and their two little piglets, Chuckie and April. But Phil, feeling himself drawn to a higher calling, insists on offering his children the chance of a good education, so he persuades his family to sell the farm and move to the city. No sooner said than done and before long the pig family have settled into their new surroundings. Phil finds a job as a car salesman, while Clara gets interested in fashion and the kids of course go to school. You wouldn’t notice anything out of the ordinary if it weren't for the fact they’re the only pigs in the neighbourhood, an area inhabited, exclusively, by human beings!

0300009033.title: One World
0300009033.description: A former pro ballplayer and his sculptor wife start a family in an unorthodox way, adopting six teenagers of various ethnic and racial backgrounds.

02176.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
02176.description: Bean is back! Join him, alongside his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady, for more zany mishaps that surround his daily life.

0300007848.title: Mi Padre El Rockero (Doblado)
0300007848.description: Lo único que quiere un chico de 12 años es una vida común y corriente, pero su papá es una estrella de rock súper popular y multimillonaria.

03948.title: Spike Team
03948.description: An evil town ruler removes all greenery and she wants one last piece of land, but a volleyball team of 6 girls plan to play her team and win it back.
